Named colors in R

Josep M (Pep) Porr
2022-01-07

All colors image

The total number of built-in color names in R is 657. The full list can be obtained with function colors() (equivalently, colours()). My goal in this project was to create a picture where all named colors can be grasped together. This is the final picture:

The code to generate it can be found in the file all_colors_plot.R.

Other information

In addition to this image, Ive included the code for three documents:

  1. Show images in Rmarkdown briefly explain how to include images in Rmarkdown documents
  2. Named colors in R Shin a simple Shiny page to explore all named colors and create palettes with them using functions colorRamp() and colorRampPalette()
  3. 20220107_color_in_r.Rmd document to test the functions used in the Shiny document above
